-Ministry of Justice  effectively coordinates between national institutions in the rule of law sector.
- 25% of Kosovo judges and 30%  of Kosovo prosecutors trained on the application of human rights stands and norms (including on the application of provisions of the Law on Protection from Discrimination);
- Law on Mediation Drafted;
--Guidelines for harmonizing judicial practices (criminal and civil field) at the Basic Courts and Court of Appeal are finalized and published/ Bulletin no 2 published and distributed.
